## Design System

- **Font**: Playfair Display (headings) + DM Sans (body)
- **Primary color**: Orange `#f97316`
- **Theme**: Dark mode — `#0a0a0f` base
- **Components**: glass cards, glow buttons, shimmer skeletons
- **Animations**: Framer Motion page transitions + micro-interactions

---

## Pages Overview

| Page             | Path              | Auth Required |
|------------------|-------------------|---------------|
| Home             | /                 | No            |
| Products         | /products         | No            |
| Product Detail   | /products/:id     | No            |
| Cart             | /cart             | No            |
| Checkout         | /checkout         | Yes (user)    |
| Profile / Orders | /profile          | Yes (user)    |
| Admin Dashboard  | /admin            | Yes (admin)   |
| Admin Products   | /admin/products   | Yes (admin)   |
| Admin Orders     | /admin/orders     | Yes (admin)   |
| Admin Users      | /admin/users      | Yes (admin)   |

